A mercenary-for-hire, he sails the skies for a
steep price. He will increase your ship's Quick.

Having Don in your active crew will increase
your ship's Dodge%.

Having Brabham in your active crew will increase

Having Hans in your active crew will increase
your ship's Magic Defense.

Having Belle in your active crew will increase

Having Khazim in your active crew will increase
the damage done by your Main Cannons.

Having Tikatika in your active crew increases

Having Domingo in your active crew increases

Having Osman in your active crew will increase

Having Kalifa in your active crew will increase
your chance of finding special items.

Having Izmael in your active crew will increase

Using the Crew Command, she will replenish your
ship's HP to full.

Using the Crew Command, she will replenish one
character's MP.

Using the Crew Command, she will max out
your Spirit Points.

Using the Crew Command, he will raise your 
ship's Attack and Defense for a short time.

Using the Crew Command, he will raise your
ship's attributes for a short period of time.

Using the Crew Command, he will double all of
your Spirit Points for one turn.

Using the Crew Command, he will reduce the
Spirit Points cost for actions for a turn.

Using the Crew Command, he will raise your
chances of attacking first for a full turn.

Having Merida in your active crew will increase
your ship's value.

Using the Crew Command, she will protect your

Using the Crew Command, he will protect your
